story:
Primitive *earthworm*: Drops of rain were falling so I took my shovel to dig up some earthworms to put them on my fishhook*.*

///

*Earthworm Jim*'s prized possession is a genuine copy of the #1 issue of *Spider-Man*. And oddly enough, *Spider-Man*'s most prized possession is a genuine first edition of *Earthworm Jim*.
